longBusinessSummary: Asahi India Glass Limited, an integrated glass and windows solutions company, manufactures and supplies various glass products in India and internationally. It operates in two segments, Automotive Glass and Float Glass. It provides various glass products for passenger vehicles, commercial vehicles, trucks, buses, railways, metros, tractors, off-highway vehicles, three wheelers, and white goods segment The company also offers float glasses, coated glasses for exteriors and interiors, processed glasses, value added glasses, and fire resistant glasses. In addition, it provides consumer glasses; and car glass repair and replacement services. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Gurugram, India.
